CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 2, 1952, pg. 11 reads: "Visitors - Mrs. Carrie Wright and her two little daughters, Laura Jane (left) and Linda Marie, of New Jersey were the guests of Mr. and Mrs. Ralph Stewart of Bricelyn Street recently. They attended the elaborate annual scholarship garden party given by the Metoka Club. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Carrie Wright, standing between daughters Laura Jane, left, and Linda Marie, right, at the Metoka Club Scholarship Garden Party, Prince Hall Temple, 157 Larimer Avenue
